						               													<description>The game consists in arranging five-word sentences from word cards divided into 5 levels of &amp;quot;sharpness&amp;quot;. The players randomly choose one of them and try to dominate the sentence with words with their level. To make it not too easy, word cards have effects that significantly affect the gameplay and allow you to plan your strategies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Classic variant: 170 cards + instruction.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Deluxe variant: 170 cards + 50 cards from the Pierwsze Namydlenie expansion + instructions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every player on their turn add one card to form a sentence and selects a new card on hand. The cards are arranged in the following order: adjective, noun, verb, noun, adverb. On the first card, more are placed, changing the sentence. The meaning of the sentence does not matter, what counts is the markings (numbers) on the cards. The resulting sentences are fun, but just an extra dose. Some cards also have additional functions that make the game easier for their owner or make it difficult for opponents. When someone dominates the sentence with his sign, he wins and the game is over.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
